    "description": "Exotica is a simulation game where you run an exotic pet shop in the city.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DO YOU LOVE EXOTIC ANIMALS TOO?</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/99effd3c248997f7ccada195b591d63b.poster.avif?t=1768817813\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/99effd3c248997f7ccada195b591d63b.webm?t=1768817813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/99effd3c248997f7ccada195b591d63b.mp4?t=1768817813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Design an amazing exotic pet shop. Bring exotic animal lovers together with these lovely creatures.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LAY OUT YOUR SHOP THE WAY YOUR WANT.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/8bbe0c4382aa96170fce07694fa3402a.poster.avif?t=1768817813\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/8bbe0c4382aa96170fce07694fa3402a.webm?t=1768817813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/8bbe0c4382aa96170fce07694fa3402a.mp4?t=1768817813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Design your shop the best you can. Do not ignore customers' requests. A satisfied customer means more customers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >START WITH LITTLE AND GROW INTO A BIG PETSHOP.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/2ab4e475a9769c97ea60e67d30bdd92a.poster.avif?t=1768817813\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/2ab4e475a9769c97ea60e67d30bdd92a.webm?t=1768817813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/2ab4e475a9769c97ea60e67d30bdd92a.mp4?t=1768817813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Don't forget to pay your bills and bank debts because it can bankrupt your shop.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BREED ANIMALS OF DIFFERENT SPECIES.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/6697147c47175c2f72aa66a3efc8b434.poster.avif?t=1768817813\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/6697147c47175c2f72aa66a3efc8b434.webm?t=1768817813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/6697147c47175c2f72aa66a3efc8b434.mp4?t=1768817813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Get more profit by breeding your animals. Rare animals are more in demand.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ARE YOU A GAMBLER?</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/0a971ea37052ac8684108a7878e7ca3b.poster.avif?t=1768817813\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/0a971ea37052ac8684108a7878e7ca3b.webm?t=1768817813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/0a971ea37052ac8684108a7878e7ca3b.mp4?t=1768817813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Whether you earn money legally or illegally is entirely up to you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HIRE AN EMPLOYEE TO LIGHTEN YOUR WORKLOAD!</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/ad71279d866fa6680784b6215d964049.poster.avif?t=1768817813\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/ad71279d866fa6680784b6215d964049.webm?t=1768817813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138580/extras/ad71279d866fa6680784b6215d964049.mp4?t=1768817813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Hire employees for your shop. Staff is the only person to help you when the shop gets crowded. But beware, employees may have phobias and waste that will damage your shop.",
